definition[0]: unable to see, move, feel etc in the normal way because you are not conscious
example[0]: She was found alive but unconscious.
example[1]: Levin was knocked unconscious by the impact.
definition[1]: a feeling or thought that is unconscious is one that you have without realizing it
example[2]: an unconscious need to be loved
definition[2]: an action that is unconscious is not deliberate
